verses.rendering:
His firstborn bull — majesty belongs to him;
his horns are the horns of a wild ox.
With them he gores the nations,
all of them, to the ends of the earth.
These are the myriads of Ephraim;
these are the thousands of Manasseh.

Of Asher he said:
Most blessed of sons is Asher;
let him be favored among his brothers,
and let him bathe his foot in oil.
